    "Sections 3.1 and 3.2 highlight how GPT-4 responds to these questions and offers detailed and relevant feedback as a possible sparring partner in student learning.",
    "Feed-forward is a proactive approach that complements traditional feedback by focusing on future learning strategies and improvements.",
    "It involves providing formative assessments along with recommendations to guide students in enhancing their future performance.",
    "Based on research question 2 and detailed in section 3.3, this study evaluates GPT-4's ability to handle formative assessments through chain-of-thought prompting.",
